{{zh-hanzi|[[共]][[匪]]}}
==Chinese==
===[[Mandarin]]===
Pinyin: gòngfěi
===Etymology===
A [[derogatory]] term for Chinese communists that was once commonly used by the [[w:Kuomintang|Nationalist forces]] led by [[w:Chiang Kai-shek|Chiang Kai-shek]].<br> 
Literally: [[共]]: [[中國|<font color="gray">中國</font>]][[共產黨|共<font color="gray">產黨</font>]], [[中国|<font color="gray">中国</font>]][[共产党|共<font color="gray">产党</font>]] = Chinese communist<br>
[[匪]]: bandit
===Noun===
#[[communist bandit]]

